      <title>独家：消息人士称中金公司今年或将削减至少10%投行人员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-may-cut-investment-banking-headcount-by-least-10-this-year-sources-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士表示，由于资本市场低迷和经济低迷使前景黯淡，中国国际金融公司（中金公司）今年可能会削减至少 10% 的投资银行员工人数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-may-cut-investment-banking-headcount-by-least-10-this-year-sources-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:05:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸战争，军政府和叛乱分子面临关键窗口期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-war-crucial-window-looms-junta-rebels-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在缅甸东南部道纳山的丛林中，来自武装少数民族的叛乱分子正在奋力阻止该国执政军政府派出的增援部队，试图夺回泰国边境的重要贸易前哨苗瓦底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-war-crucial-window-looms-junta-rebels-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:04:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国 LGBTQ 活动在许可证斗争后在街头落户</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-lgbtq-event-finds-home-streets-after-permit-struggle-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国年度 LGBTQ 聚会的组织者周二表示，首尔酷儿文化节今年将在首都街头举行，此前市政府拒绝了他们在四个地点举办活动的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-lgbtq-event-finds-home-streets-after-permit-struggle-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员称，伊朗运输石油的能力依赖马来西亚的服务提供商</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/irans-capacity-move-oil-reliant-malaysian-providers-us-official-says-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部一名高级官员周二表示，美国认为伊朗运输石油的能力依赖于位于马来西亚的服务提供商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/irans-capacity-move-oil-reliant-malaysian-providers-us-official-says-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>柬埔寨表示，中国资助的新湄公河运河将把通过越南的航运减少70%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-will-cut-shipping-through-vietnam-by-70-with-new-china-funded-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柬埔寨副总理告诉路透社，由于中国出资 17 亿美元升级连接湄公河流域和柬埔寨海岸的运河，柬埔寨计划将通过越南港口的航运减少 70%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-will-cut-shipping-through-vietnam-by-70-with-new-china-funded-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官表示，Primark 所有者将提高解释食品业务优点的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/primark-owner-raise-game-explaining-merits-food-businesses-ceo-says-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Primark 的母公司英国联合食品公司首席执行官告诉路透社，该公司在向投资者解释其食品业务的战略逻辑、增长潜力和价值方面做得不够好，必须做得更好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/primark-owner-raise-game-explaining-merits-food-businesses-ceo-says-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行认为没有必要加息但警惕价格风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australias-central-bank-holds-interest-rates-vigilant-inflation-risks-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行行长周二表示，利率在连续第六个月保持稳定后处于正确水平，但警告称，通胀风险正在上升，这表明政策不太可能很快放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australias-central-bank-holds-interest-rates-vigilant-inflation-risks-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1990年以来澳大利亚利率变化</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australian-interest-rate-changes-since-1990-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚储备银行周二在政策会议后将现金利率维持在 4.35% 不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australian-interest-rate-changes-since-1990-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:43:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行上调通胀预期，预计 2025 年前不会降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australia-central-bank-lifts-inflation-forecasts-assumes-no-rate-cuts-until-2025-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透悉尼5月7日 - 澳大利亚央行周二大幅上调总体通胀预期，并排除了今年降息的可能性，这表明借款人可能要到2025年才会看到利率下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/australia-central-bank-lifts-inflation-forecasts-assumes-no-rate-cuts-until-2025-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:41:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，苹果正在开发用于数据中心的人工智能芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-working-ai-chips-data-centers-wsj-reports-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》周一援引知情人士的话报道称，苹果正在开发自己的芯片，用于在数据中心运行人工智能软件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-working-ai-chips-data-centers-wsj-reports-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:26:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
